# Worksheet config

⚠️ IMPORTANT! Copy this file to `rules/config.md` (gitignored) and fill in your values. This file is the single source of truth for both personal configuration and location-to-system mappings — edit only this file when changing personal details, project codes, or client sites.

## Identity

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| Name | Your Full Name |
| Email | your@email.com |

## Companies

Throughout this plugin, **CLIENT** refers to the client timesheet system and **EMPLOYER** refers to the employer's administration tool. The names below are the canonical values used everywhere these placeholders appear.

| Name | Value |
|---|---|
| CLIENT | Your client's timesheet system |
| EMPLOYER | Your employer's administration tool |

## Contacts

| Name | Role | Email |
|---|---|---|
| Admin contact name | EMPLOYER administration | admin@company.com |

## Project codes

| Project | Code |
|---|---|
| Default (CLIENT on-site / remote) | Client-YourName |
| Meetup | Meetup |
| Leave / Sick | Verlof / Leave |
| Vacation | Vakantie / Vacation |
| National Holiday | Feestdag / National Holiday |

## Calendar

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| Work calendar | `Work` (Google Calendar) |

